{"tid":1924801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國天才抗疫策略：「物競天擇，適者生存」，做好心理準備面對生離死別","createTime":"2020-03-14T02:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T03:47:56.000Z","uid":109780,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3747053de082ce8e9fc3cd9d5e942ccec35697df","tid":1924801,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:07:22.000Z","msg":"英國首相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）在當地時間12日下午宣布，英國正式進入第二階段「<br />\nDelay 延宕期」。旅英親子作家QQmei聽完首相的發言後表示，「講白話點就是『要有心<br />\n理準備會死更多人』」、「說好的Keep calm and carry on（保持冷靜並繼續前進）呢？<br />\n」也不禁羨慕台灣的防疫措施，「台灣政府真的做得很好很好，請大家珍惜再珍惜。」<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎在歐洲擴散的速度超乎想像，愛爾蘭、法國等國紛紛宣布關閉學校，本以為英國<br />\n會跟進其他國家的停課政策，想不到強生卻說，「現階段不停課」，其他有疑似症狀者「<br />\n請自行在家隔離」，除非病情太過嚴重，否則不需要打給醫療緊急專線1111。對此，<br />\nQQmei在臉書表示，「這是一場物競天擇、適者生存的防疫」，強生也坦言，「接下來可<br />\n能有更多家庭失去摯愛」，言下之意就是請國人做好心理準備，將會出現更多確診病例甚<br />\n至死亡數。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200313/1666527.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200313%2F1666527.htm&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=bca5240b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200313/1666527.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日落國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"10d46895b396770d433a11d051b600dec8bff37f","tid":1924801,"uid":219529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:11:00.000Z","msg":"英國同日本做法相似，但最小日本人會帶口罩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01187877ae9a1a8bec352cee70d8e4f7f6e93d6e","tid":1924801,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:11:19.000Z","msg":"天黑國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPmi9do.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPmi9do.jpg&h=4c20e3e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":